The paper deals with learning optimal strategies for agents in ad exchanges, which involves game theory, machine learning, and information retrieval. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.GT (Game Theory and Economics), followed by cs.LG (Machine Learning), cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence), cs.IR (Information Retrieval), and cs.DS (Data Structures and Algorithms).
